  "prompt": "How old is Percy Jackson in the movie?",
  "response": "In the **\"Percy Jackson\" movies**, the character **Percy Jackson** is portrayed as a **16-year-old high school student**. This is a slight age adjustment from the original book series by Rick Riordan, where Percy starts at **12 years old** in the first book, **\"The Lightning Thief.\"** The movies aged him up to better fit the teenage demographic of the actors and the target audience for the films.\n\n- **\"Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief\" (2010):** Percy is **16 years old**.\n- **\"Percy Jackson: Sea of Monsters\" (2013):** Percy remains around **16-17 years old**, continuing his adventures as a high school student.\n\nThis adjustment allows for a more mature portrayal of Percy\u2019s character and aligns with the casting of actors who were teenagers or young adults at the time of filming.",
